text: Dr Fong Seng Yew is caring and very generous with his time. He takes the time and trouble to explain clearly the different drugs and treatment options. His analysis is good and updated.

Great experience and I highly recommend it to anyone seeking medical care in the area. The physician, Dr. Fong, was accommodating and puts the patient first, which I appreciated. He was also very attentive and showed great consideration towards my opinions and concerns. Service was good and the price was very affordable for a general practitioner.

Do note that the clinic only accepts cash or Paynow as payment options.
Very experienced Doctor. Highly recommended. Can communicate well with elderly as he can speak dialects.

doctor ok, but the clinic assistant is rude and uncouth. With a long black face.

Highly recommended!
